76%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/e2410/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 237w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/4d3d4/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 475w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 949w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/5a523/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px\" srcSet=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/e2410/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 237w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/4d3d4/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 475w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 949w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/5a523/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg\" alt=\"SABJ Book of Lists - Top Advertising Agencies in San Antonio\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/e2410/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 237w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/4d3d4/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 475w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 949w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/5a523/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px\" srcset=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/e2410/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 237w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/4d3d4/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 475w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 949w,\n/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/5a523/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/88c31322c3860aeff98778d81509a12c/353b5/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists.jpg\" alt=\"SABJ Book of Lists - Top Advertising Agencies in San Antonio\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The PM Group is proud to be featured as the 2020 top advertising agency in the San Antonio Book of Lists. For over 31 years, we have grown to become the advertising leader in our community. The agency’s <strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/capabilities/\">client roster</a></strong> spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. Through the PM Group&#8217;s <a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/companies/\"><strong>affiliated companies</strong></a> we function as a full-service agency helping our clients expand their business and reach new audiences. In addition, the agency also hosts an annual Charity Fun-Raiser Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years alone, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over <strong><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/community/\">$12 million for these charities</a></strong>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We are honored to be recognized by the <strong><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/\">San Antonio Business Journal</a></strong> in their Book of Lists and look forward to 2020 being a year of opportunities to continue to grow in the advertising industry.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Previously, the PM Group has been recognized as San Antonio&#8217;s largest advertising agency in <strong><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/subscriber-only/2016/08/19/advertising-agencies.html\">2015</a>, <a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/subscriber-only/2017/08/04/advertising-agencies.html\">2016</a>, <a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/subscriber-only/2018/08/03/largest-san-antonio-advertising.html\">2017, </a><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/subscriber-only/2019/09/22/largest-san-antonio-advertising.html\">2018</a></strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/sanantonio/subscriber-only/2020/08/07/advertising-agencies-revenue.html\">2019</a></strong>.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Ranked as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Ranked as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency","url":"/san-antonio-largest-advertising-agency/"}],"title":"The PM Group Recognized as Largest Advertising Agency in San Antonio","metaDesc":"The San Antonio Business Journal recognized The PM Group as the largest advertising agency in San Antonio based on annual gross advertising revenues.","focuskw":"largest advertising agency","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM Group Recognized as Largest Advertising Agency in San Antonio","opengraphDescription":"The San Antonio Business Journal recognized The PM Group as the largest advertising agency in San Antonio based on annual gross advertising revenues.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"SABJ Book of Lists - Top Advertising Agencies in San Antonio","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists-Square.png","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists-Square-300x300.png 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Image-2.21.20-SABJ-Book-of-Lists-Square-150x150.png 1